Class NumberedPager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.UIObject
      • com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.Widget
        • com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.Composite
          • com.google.gwt.user.cellview.client.AbstractPager
            • com.github.gwtbootstrap.client.ui.NumberedPager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasId, HasStyle, IsResponsive, HasAttachHandlers, HasHandlers, EventListener, HasVisibility, IsRenderable, IsWidget

    public class NumberedPager
extends AbstractPager
implements HasStyle, IsResponsive, HasId
    A pager for controlling a HasRows using Pagination. Just bind the NumberedPager using NumberedPager.setDisplay to some HasRows implementation like CellTable or DataGrid, and the pager is automatically generated fully working.
